	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Hac transiens <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l294" cert="high">Locarnensium</placeName> christianorum nuncius contulit mecum de negocio; inter alia dixit se habere in mandatis, ut christiani alium mitterent statim ad dominos Tigurinos, [qui] quicquid actum in comitiis esset, <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l294" cert="high">Locarnum</placeName> refferet.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sed quia longum est iter perdifficileque, decrevimus inter nos, hinc ut ille <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l294" cert="high">Locarnum</placeName> quam citius accederet, ego vero ad te scriberem hunc in modum, nempe si videris illorum rem perditum iri, velis propriis sumptibus nostris nuncium huc curiam mittere ad Filippum Gallicium, cum quo ego egi, ut et ipse ad me <placeName ref="l96" cert="high">Clavenam</placeName> proprium nuncium mitteret cum literis tuis.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Hoc autem dicco, si cognoveris <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l294" cert="high">Locarnensibus</placeName> periculum vitę aut naufragium substantie totius imminere, sin minus, literas tuas solito more mittas ad <persName type="auto_name">Gallicium</persName>, qui mihi eas reddendas curabit.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quicquid autem exposueris, si opus fuerit, hoc meo nomine a domino <persName type="auto_name">Sebastiano</persName> petes.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Inclusas autem domino <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8101" cert="high">Lelio</persName> reddendas curare digneris.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale, mi clarissime vir et domine colendissime.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l98" cert="high">Curię</placeName> pridie kalendas decembris 1554.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dominationis et humanitatis tę deditissimum mancipium <persName ref="p19255" cert="high">Antonius Marius Besutus</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Pietate, doctrina ac moribus clarissimo viro domino <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Henrico Bulingero</persName>, antistiti Tigurino, domino suo colendissimo.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
	</text>
